  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK991">
<l>eṇpatattā leyta leḷiteṉpa yārmāṭṭum</l>
<l>paṇpuṭaimai yeṉṉum vaḻakku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one is easy of access to all, it will be easy for one to obtain the virtue called goodness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
